      "type": "text",
      "data": {
        "text": "**5.** A well-versed partnership would know the meaning of a defensive signal in this situation, but you can determine the correct play without an agreement. You should play the club queen to alert East to your ability to ruff a spade. (A suit-preference signal while giving the ruff may produce a second spade ruff.)"
